{"tid":791232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★蛇齋餅糉再升級？多名建制區議員派現金","createTime":"2018-08-23T15:32:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T03:07:07.000Z","uid":19454,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"be091649cdb15ebcfba675f6f04f1acf73e2e5fa","tid":791232,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T15:32:32.000Z","msg":"建制派經常被外界批評用「蛇齋餅稯」去討好市民，爭取選民支持，近日更疑似出現「升級版」。觀塘區多名建制派區議員同地區人士都同觀塘民聯會(觀民會)合作，為選區內嘅中、小學生提供<span style=\"color: red;\">300蚊港紙</span>嘅現金開學津貼，未知今次「派錢」同下年嘅區議會換屆選舉係咪有關係呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n民建聯(民記)觀塘區議員歐陽均諾今個星期一(20日)喺Facebook貼出海報，話有「學生開學津貼」，凡居於佢啟業選區嘅18/19年度在學中、小學生都可以申請，中籤者<span style=\"color: red;\">可獲發300蚊現金</span>。海報上印有歐陽均諾嘅辦事處地址同電話，以及觀塘民聯會嘅地址同電話，但就未見列明主辦同協辦嘅字眼。另外，選舉管理委員會建議嘅新增選區安泰邨，有名為「安泰居民會」嘅組織亦喺網上列出今次津貼計劃，但海報就列明是由觀民會主辦，同時印埋居民會總幹事林瑋嘅大頭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180823/bkn-20180823185010954-0823_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180823%2Fbkn-20180823185010954-0823_00822_001.html&d=RzP3LsgGeiXY4iqKetPgmjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=fb7d8e32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180823/bkn-20180823185010954-0823_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"47c93ea872cc66a10375f730613182371a8c49ef","tid":791232,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T15:32:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"565a37afc9b19422e9b38a9cc5d7f109f9232cf6","tid":791232,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T15:36:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9cf3b641597bd5e6a3caceabdc42dac2002e318","tid":791232,"uid":745,"like":1,"